<emphasis bold="true" box="[1392,1568,1358,1387]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">Distribution.</emphasis>
Sipora and North and South Pagai Is, MentawaiIs; population on Siberut I likely belongs to this species.
</paragraph>
</caption>
